<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٣٤١ - قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5495">أَبُو عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>وَقَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3481">الْأُوَيْسِيُّ </a>حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5533">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6932">يَحْيَى بْنِ سَعِيدٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2778">وَشَرِيكٍ </a>سَمِعَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> <span class="c2">«رَفَعَ يَدَيْهِ حَتَّى رَأَيْتُ بَيَاضَ إِبْطَيْهِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>